      "raceComments": "{\"comment\":\"7. COOLHAND CHLOE goes very well at the course with two wins and a placing from six starts. Missed the frame latest (19.22) when sixth over 350m at Q Straight in a Grade 5. Looks a key chance on best form. 1. GYPSY GIRL PEARL was safely held last time out, finishing seventh at this track over 520m behind Bentley Kristoff (30.72) in a Grade 4/5. The form from her last run stacks up well. Expected to run well. 4. MISS BEAR steps out for the first time at this circuit. Scored in one of the quickest times on the card (25.18) latest, winning by 9 lengths at Q Lakeside in a Grade 5. Strong form has emerged from her last run. Hard to fault her recent form and can win again. 2. FIVE BIRDIES is fresh from a short break and ready to run well.\",\"runners\":[7,1,4,2],\"exclusive\":false}",
